                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/2644</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul General <gloss type="from">Sammons</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate General</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-03T12:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 3, 1917, noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Chinese Commissioner of Foreign Affairs states confidently Vice President Feng
                    and all local military and naval forces agree oppose monarchy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sammons</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
